{
    "poem_title": "LA PROMENADE CHAMPÊTRE",
    "author": "Maurice Rollinat",
    "structure": "suite périodique",
    "year": "1877",
    "manually_checked": false,
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": 1,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Mai, le plus amoureux des mois,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Fleurit et parfume les haies.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Allons-nous-en dans les chênaies,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Égarons-nous au fond des bois !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Cherchons la source et les clairières,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Dormons à l'ombre du bouleau ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Un bon soleil ami de l'eau",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Sourit aux flaques des carrières.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mai, le plus amoureux des mois,\nFleurit et parfume les haies.\nAllons-nous-en dans les chênaies,\nÉgarons-nous au fond des bois !\nCherchons la source et les clairières,\nDormons à l'ombre du bouleau ;\nUn bon soleil ami de l'eau\nSourit aux flaques des carrières."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et tous deux nous nous enfonçons",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Dans la campagne ! et, champs, prairies,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Brandes, mares et métairies",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Tout ça rêve entre les buissons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Intrigués par notre costume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Les bœufs, avec un œil dormant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Nous considèrent gravement",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "En léchant leur mufle qui fume.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et tous deux nous nous enfonçons\nDans la campagne ! et, champs, prairies,\nBrandes, mares et métairies\nTout ça rêve entre les buissons.\nIntrigués par notre costume,\nLes bœufs, avec un œil dormant\nNous considèrent gravement\nEn léchant leur mufle qui fume."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Mélancolique et cher pays,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "À nous tes petites auberges,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ta Gargilesse humble et tes berges",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Si pleines d'ombre et de fouillis !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Nous deux nous sommes les touristes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Familiers de tes casse-cou,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Et nous adorons le coucou",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Qui pleure dans tes bois si tristes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mélancolique et cher pays,\nÀ nous tes petites auberges,\nTa Gargilesse humble et tes berges\nSi pleines d'ombre et de fouillis !\nNous deux nous sommes les touristes\nFamiliers de tes casse-cou,\nEt nous adorons le coucou\nQui pleure dans tes bois si tristes."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "— Traversons la cour du fermier :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Au fond, le chien dort sous un frêne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Lentement un crapaud se traîne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Horrible et doux sur le fumier.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Ici, la cane barboteuse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Glousse devant un soupirail ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Là, des bergers frottent leur ail",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Sur une croûte raboteuse.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "— Traversons la cour du fermier :\nAu fond, le chien dort sous un frêne,\nLentement un crapaud se traîne\nHorrible et doux sur le fumier.\nIci, la cane barboteuse\nGlousse devant un soupirail ;\nLà, des bergers frottent leur ail\nSur une croûte raboteuse."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Tiens ! voici venir chevauchant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Assis sur des sacs de farine,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Le grand Pierre à qui Mathurine",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Songe plus d'une fois au champ.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Insoucieux, il se balance,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Jetant sa voix claire à l'écho,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Déhanché sur son bourriquot,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Et tout rempli de nonchalance.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tiens ! voici venir chevauchant,\nAssis sur des sacs de farine,\nLe grand Pierre à qui Mathurine\nSonge plus d'une fois au champ.\nInsoucieux, il se balance,\nJetant sa voix claire à l'écho,\nDéhanché sur son bourriquot,\nEt tout rempli de nonchalance."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Angélique, au bord du lavoir,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "À genoux dans l'herbe et la mousse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Tape et tord le linge qui mousse.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "C'est tout un plaisir de la voir !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Il sonne en vain le battoir jaune,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Les grenouilles n'en ont pas peur.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Dans une sereine torpeur,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Elles songent au pied d'un aune.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Angélique, au bord du lavoir,\nÀ genoux dans l'herbe et la mousse,\nTape et tord le linge qui mousse.\nC'est tout un plaisir de la voir !\nIl sonne en vain le battoir jaune,\nLes grenouilles n'en ont pas peur.\nDans une sereine torpeur,\nElles songent au pied d'un aune."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Que nous font les terrains vaseux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Puisque chantent les pastourelles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Et qu'on peut voir dans les nids frêles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Le mystère des petits œufs ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "La pente est rude, mais la roche",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Où le pied se pose au hasard",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "S'émeraude avec le lézard,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Et voici que la Creuse est proche !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que nous font les terrains vaseux\nPuisque chantent les pastourelles,\nEt qu'on peut voir dans les nids frêles\nLe mystère des petits œufs ?\nLa pente est rude, mais la roche\nOù le pied se pose au hasard\nS'émeraude avec le lézard,\nEt voici que la Creuse est proche !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Là-bas, Margot jacasse avec",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 58,
                    "line_text": "Autant de feu qu'une dévote,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 59,
                    "line_text": "Elle court, sautille et pivote,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 60,
                    "line_text": "Hochant la queue, ouvrant le bec.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 61,
                    "line_text": "Impossible d'être plus drôle !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 62,
                    "line_text": "Elle danse, et va s'amusant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 63,
                    "line_text": "D'un beau petit caillou luisant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 64,
                    "line_text": "Et d'un brin d'herbe qui la frôle.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Là-bas, Margot jacasse avec\nAutant de feu qu'une dévote,\nElle court, sautille et pivote,\nHochant la queue, ouvrant le bec.\nImpossible d'être plus drôle !\nElle danse, et va s'amusant\nD'un beau petit caillou luisant,\nEt d'un brin d'herbe qui la frôle."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 65,
                    "line_text": "Du fond des chemins oubliés",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 66,
                    "line_text": "Où notre semelle s'attache,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 67,
                    "line_text": "Nous voyons la vieille patache",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Qui roule entre les peupliers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Quand les coups de fouets aiguillonnent",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 70,
                    "line_text": "Les pauvres chevaux courbatus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 71,
                    "line_text": "Sur les colliers hauts et pointus,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 72,
                    "line_text": "Comme les grelots carillonnent !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Du fond des chemins oubliés\nOù notre semelle s'attache,\nNous voyons la vieille patache\nQui roule entre les peupliers.\nQuand les coups de fouets aiguillonnent\nLes pauvres chevaux courbatus,\nSur les colliers hauts et pointus,\nComme les grelots carillonnent !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 73,
                    "line_text": "Et la hutte en chaume terreux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 74,
                    "line_text": "Abri des petites bergères,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 75,
                    "line_text": "Est au milieu de ses fougères",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 76,
                    "line_text": "Hospitalière aux amoureux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 77,
                    "line_text": "Dans un mystère délectable,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 78,
                    "line_text": "Las de courir et de causer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 79,
                    "line_text": "Nous venons nous y reposer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 80,
                    "line_text": "Sur la paille qui sent l'étable.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et la hutte en chaume terreux,\nAbri des petites bergères,\nEst au milieu de ses fougères\nHospitalière aux amoureux.\nDans un mystère délectable,\nLas de courir et de causer,\nNous venons nous y reposer,\nSur la paille qui sent l'étable."
        }
    ],
